children.text: "Set as Alarm" command will not affect existing alarms, only the new ones you create. You can delete existing alarm and create new one.

Go to Home Screen > Press Menu button on your phone > Add > Widget > Choose "Baby Sounds Free" > Choose a sound.

OR

Go to Home Screen > Long press on desktop > Widget > Choose "Baby Sounds Free" > Choose a sound.
